1
00:00:06,236 --> 00:00:07,391
Where do I like to shop?
我喜欢去哪买东西?

2
00:00:07,781 --> 00:00:10,423
Shopping is not my, my sport.
购物可不是我的...我的运动.

3
00:00:10,764 --> 00:00:13,626
I, I am really not the guy to talk about shopping.
我,实在不是那个谈论购物的人.

4
00:00:13,580 --> 00:00:15,250
I have a daughter who's 12.
我有个12岁的女儿,

5
00:00:15,332 --> 00:00:17,280
and I found I enjoy shopping with her now.
我发现我现在喜欢跟她一起去买东西.

6
00:00:17,398 --> 00:00:18,290
She's getting old enough.
她已经长大了.

7
00:00:18,433 --> 00:00:21,068
We like similar things or we like totally opposite things,
我跟她有时喜欢相同的东西,有时截然相反,

8
00:00:21,208 --> 00:00:22,870
but it's fun together.
但在一起很开心.

9
00:00:23,001 --> 00:00:25,495
If we can find a mall that isn't as crowded,
如果可以找到不太拥挤的购物中心的话,

10
00:00:25,600 --> 00:00:26,600
we'll go there,
我们会去,

11
00:00:26,622 --> 00:00:28,799
but most of the time we go to neighborhood shops.
但大多数时候我们去社区商店.

12
00:00:28,991 --> 00:00:29,938
Sometimes I like to shop.
我有时喜欢买东西.

13
00:00:30,151 --> 00:00:33,407
Usually I prefer shopping from catalogs than going to the mall. 
通常我更喜欢邮购, 而不是去购物中心,

14
00:00:33,731 --> 00:00:35,388
because there are too many people.
因为那里人太多.

15
00:00:35,644 --> 00:00:37,507
Who shops for my clothes?
谁给我买衣服?

16
00:00:37,693 --> 00:00:40,858
Er, I shop for my own clothes.
Er,我自己买我自己的衣服.

17
00:00:41,027 --> 00:00:42,756
I only shop when I need something.
我只在有需要时才去买东西.

18
00:00:42,912 --> 00:00:43,998
I don't shop for pleasure.
我买东西不是为了休闲娱乐.

19
00:00:44,222 --> 00:00:46,651
When we were younger, shopping was our recreation,
当我们年轻的时候, 买东西是我们的娱乐活动,

20
00:00:46,816 --> 00:00:51,328
but now I do what I have to do and I don't do it any other time.
但现在我做我不得不做的事情, 而且我在其他时候不会去做它.

21
00:00:51,510 --> 00:00:54,721
I'm a real bohemian, so we've been married for six years 
我是个真正的波西米亚人,所以我们结婚六年了,

22
00:00:54,913 --> 00:00:58,881
and I don't think I've bought any of my own clothes in six years, if that answers your question.
我想我还未给自己买过一件衣服在这六年中, 如果那回答了你的问题.

23
00:00:59,190 --> 00:01:00,058
Automotive parts.
汽车零部件.

24
00:01:00,390 --> 00:01:02,317
I'm big on automotive parts, sometimes.
我喜欢买汽车零部件, 有时.

25
00:01:02,497 --> 00:01:03,210
The food shopping.
购买食品.

26
00:01:03,300 --> 00:01:04,500
My wife does all the food shopping.
我妻子购买所有的食品.

27
00:01:04,728 --> 00:01:10,953
I'm from Frankfurt, Germany, and we have a flea market every week, um, near the river. 
我来自德国的法兰克福, 那儿每周都有跳蚤市场, um,在河边.

28
00:01:11,234 --> 00:01:12,545
I like to buy there.
我喜欢到那里买东西.

29
00:01:12,763 --> 00:01:15,861
Sometimes I go shopping even if I don't want to find anything myself.
有时我去逛商店, 即使我不想给自己买任何东西.

30
00:01:16,009 --> 00:01:20,300
If a friend needs something, we just walk around and look at clothes
如果有个朋友需要买什么, 我们就会走来走去, 看看衣服

31
00:01:21,200 --> 00:01:26,778
and you know, and talk and hang out, sometimes it is a social activity.
and you know, 聊天和呆在一起, 有时这是一种社交活动.

32
00:01:27,317 --> 00:01:30,769
I prefer, er, family-owned small businesses
我更喜欢,er,家庭经营的小店,

33
00:01:30,957 --> 00:01:32,706
'cause I think, um, 
因为我认为,um,

34
00:01:32,892 --> 00:01:36,021
there's a much more human quality involved in shopping in those stores.
在那种店买东西更富有人情味.

35
00:01:36,224 --> 00:01:40,387
I think it's vital to, to keep those kind of community centers going. 
我认为让这类社区中心继续运转非常重要.

36
00:01:40,629 --> 00:01:47,079
I think the biggest mistake they've made in all around the world is they think that centralizing shopping has become something that makes sense.
我觉得全世界的人都犯了一个极大的错误, 他们认为集中购物相当明智.

